      <lg xml:id="TolE0120">
<l>avaṟṟuḷ</l>
<l>iṉṉi ṉikara māvi ṉiṟuti</l>
<l>muṉṉark keṭuta lurittu mākum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>And those indeed [like]</l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">iṉ, vaṟṟu, attu, am,</foreign></l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">oṉ, āṉ, akku, ikku</foreign> [and]</l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">aṉ</foreign> including yet other words</l>
<l>are said to be such empty words.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
